<h3 id="lecture-videos">Lecture Videos</h3>

<p>This week we are going to the continue talking about strategic games and Nash equilibria. Our focus will be on “best responses” a concept that is needed to solve more complicated games with many players and actions.</p>

<p>In the first video, I give you a motivating example, the formal definition of best responses and then some illustrations. 
<br /><br /></p>

